Continue working around the edges, left to right, top to bottom, right to left and bottom to top. While sealing the edges, keep the MonoKote pulled taut so that when you finish tacking down the edges, the covering is smooth and wrinkle free. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c5/Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/c5/Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet2.jpg/aid1389046-v4-728px-Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

If you see wrinkles developing, stop and carefully peel up the edges, using the ironing tool to loosen the adhesive if necessary, and pull tightly while smoothing the MonoKote, until the wrinkles are eliminated. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4c/Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/4/4c/Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet3.jpg/aid1389046-v4-728px-Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Once the edges are covered, go back to the top and run the iron over the entire surface, working from the top down. Alternately, you can do this part with a hot air gun to avoid scratching the new finish. Either way, avoid overheating and loosening the edges or you will create wrinkles. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/74/Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/7/74/Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet4.jpg/aid1389046-v4-728px-Apply-MonoKote-Step-5Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
